        <http://example.org/tennis/player/Rafael_Nadal> ;
    prov1:evidenceText "At the 2025 Miami Open, Djokovic beat lucky loser Camilo Ugo Carabelli in the third round to claim his record 411th career main draw win at the Masters 1000 level, surpassing Nadal's previous record of 410.[309]" ;
    prov1:sourceURL "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Novak_Djokovic"^^xsd:anyURI .

