        <http://example.org/tennis/player/Rafael_Nadal> ;
    prov1:evidenceText "At Monte Carlo he lost to Novak Djokovic in straight sets in the semi finals,[266] at Barcelona he lost to Fognini in the quarterfinals[267] and at Madrid he lost the final to Andy Murray in straight sets, resulting in his dropping out of the top five for the first time since 2005.[268][269]" ;
    prov1:sourceURL "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rafael_Nadal"^^xsd:anyURI .

<http://example.org/tennis/player/Frances_Tiafoe> a onto:Player ;
