        <http://example.org/tennis/player/Nikola_Miloje> ;
    prov1:evidenceText "He received wildcards at the Mexican Open, where he lost to eventual champion Alexander Zverev in the first round;[49] at the Barcelona Open, where he lost to Frances Tiafoe in the first round;[50] and at the Andalucía Open, where he defeated Nikola Miloje" ;
    prov1:sourceURL "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carlos_Alcaraz"^^xsd:anyURI .

<http://example.org/tennis/player/Kevin_Anderson> a onto:Player ;
