        <http://example.org/tennis/player/Roger_Federer_172> ;
    prov1:evidenceText "Five weeks later, he beat Kevin Anderson in the fourth round in five sets, and then went on to claim his third Wimbledon title with a win over Roger Federer.[172]" ;
    prov1:sourceURL "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Novak_Djokovic"^^xsd:anyURI .

