    prov1:evidenceText "- \"Daniil Medvedev beats Rafael Nadal to set up ATP Finals clash with Dominic Thiem\".",
        "Daniil Medvedev defeated Novak Djokovic in the final, 6–4, 6–4, 6–4 to win the men's singles tennis title at the 2021 US Open.[1]",
        "He then won his ninth Australian Open title and 18th major overall, defeating Daniil Medvedev in the final.[240]",
        "He won his second Australian Open title, 21st major title and 90th ATP title beating Daniil Medvedev in a five-set final, coming back from two sets down.[349" ;
