    prov1:evidenceText "- \"US Open: Kei Nishikori beats Novak Djokovic in the semi-finals\".",
        "At the French Open, Nadal beat Kei Nishikori and Roger Federer (their first meeting at the tournament since 2011) en route to the final, dropping only one set en route.",
        "Following an early loss at Barcelona to Martin Kližan, he showed improvement at the Madrid Open by beating Kei Nishikori—his first top 20 win in 10 months—but lost to Kyle Edmund in the second round.[201][202]" ;
    prov1:sourceURL "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Novak_Djokovic"^^xsd:anyURI,
