    prov1:evidenceText "- \"Djokovic Beats Tsitsipas For Madrid Title, Tying Nadal's Masters 1000 Record\".",
        "At the ATP Finals, Nadal beat Tsitsipas and Medvedev in the round-robin stage, but failed to progress to the semi-finals.[324]",
        "By defeating world No. 3 Stefanos Tsitsipas in the third round, Carlos Alcaraz became the youngest man to beat a top 3 ranked-player in singles at the US Open since the inception of the ATP rankings in 1973." ;
