    prov1:evidenceText "\"Carlos Alcaraz Recently Beat Nadal and Djokovic on Clay.",
        "\"French Open 2017 Final AS IT HAPPENED: Rafael Nadal beats Stan Wawrinka in stunning win\".",
        "\"Nadal beats Djokovic to put Spain through\".",
