        "- \"Monte Carlo Masters: Rafael Nadal beats Albert Ramos-Vinolas for record 10th title\".",
        "- \"Nadal Beats Djokovic To Win Ninth Rome Title\".",
        "- \"Nadal Beats Djokovic to Win U.S. Open\".",
